Rules.InvariantScript:
If(
    cmpPageCount = 1,
    Set(
        cmpPageCount,
        CountRows(cmp_Carousel.GalleryContent)
    ),
    Set(
        cmpPageCount,
        cmpPageCount - 1
    )
)

If(
    cmpPageCount = CountRows(cmp_Carousel.GalleryContent),
    cmp_Carousel.OnClose(),
    Set(
        cmpPageCount,
        cmpPageCount + 1
    )
)
